SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE ("media_attachments"."status_id" IS NOT ? OR "media_attachments"."scheduled_status_id" IS NOT ?) AND "media_attachments"."account_id" = $? ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC LIMIT $?
SELECT "media_attachments".* FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" IN ($?, $?) ORDER BY "media_attachments"."id" ASC

SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "bookmarks" ON "bookmarks"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND "bookmarks"."account_id" = $? ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $?

SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "favourites" ON "favourites"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND "favourites"."account_id" = $? ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $?
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND "statuses"."account_id" = $? ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $?

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."uri" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS ? AND "statuses"."account_id" = $? AND "statuses"."in_reply_to_id" = $? AND "statuses"."visibility" IN ($?, $?) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $?
SELECT "tags".* FROM "tags" INNER JOIN "accounts_tags" ON "tags"."id" = "accounts_tags"."tag_id" WHERE "accounts_tags"."account_id" = $?
